2. You  are  not allowed to @{u}gain money@{uu} with the spreading of the package. A
   charge for your costs (for discs, etc.) is allowed as long as the amount
   of 5,00 DM is not passed.

3. If you @{u}change@{uu} programs of the package, you are @{u}not allowed@{uu} to give those
   to  others.  You  are only allowed to give the package to others @{u}without@{uu}
   any @{u}changes@{uu} and @{u}without@{uu} the @{u}keyfile@{uu}.

4. Fred   Fish   is   explicit   allowed   to   put  this  package  in  his
